    Public Function CheckSchemeType(ByVal v_lFinancePlanCnt As Integer, ByVal v_lFinancePlanVersion As Integer, ByRef r_sSchemeType As String, ByRef r_lPFPaymentMethod_cnt As Integer) As Integer

        Dim result As Integer = 0
        Try

            result = gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMTrue

            ' Retrieve in house status for associated scheme
            m_oDatabase.Parameters.Clear()

            ' Finance plan cnt
            m_lReturn = m_oDatabase.Parameters.Add(sName:="financeplancnt", vValue:=gPMFunctions.ToSafeString(v_lFinancePlanCnt), iDirection:=gPMConstants.PMEParameterDirection.PMParamInput, iDataType:=gPMConstants.PMEDataType.PMLong)
            If m_lReturn <> gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMTrue Then
                Return m_lReturn
            End If

            ' Finance plan version
            m_lReturn = m_oDatabase.Parameters.Add(sName:="financeplanversion", vValue:=gPMFunctions.ToSafeString(v_lFinancePlanVersion), iDirection:=gPMConstants.PMEParameterDirection.PMParamInput, iDataType:=gPMConstants.PMEDataType.PMLong)
            If m_lReturn <> gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMTrue Then
                Return m_lReturn
            End If

            ' Is in house, return value
            m_lReturn = m_oDatabase.Parameters.Add(sName:="PFScheme_Type_Code", vValue:=gPMFunctions.ToSafeString(0), iDirection:=gPMConstants.PMEParameterDirection.PMParamOutput, iDataType:=gPMConstants.PMEDataType.PMString)
            If m_lReturn <> gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMTrue Then
                Return m_lReturn
            End If

            ' Is in house, return value
            m_lReturn = m_oDatabase.Parameters.Add(sName:="PFPaymentMethod_cnt", vValue:=gPMFunctions.ToSafeString(0), iDirection:=gPMConstants.PMEParameterDirection.PMParamOutput, iDataType:=gPMConstants.PMEDataType.PMLong)
            If m_lReturn <> gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMTrue Then
                Return m_lReturn
            End If

            ' Execute the procedure
            m_lReturn = m_oDatabase.SQLAction(sSQL:=ACCheckSchemeTypeSQL, sSQLName:=ACCheckSchemeTypeName, bStoredProcedure:=ACCheckSchemeTypeStored)
            If m_lReturn <> gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMTrue Then
                Return m_lReturn
            End If

            ' Retrieve the return value
            r_sSchemeType = gPMFunctions.NullToString(m_oDatabase.Parameters.Item("PFScheme_Type_code").Value)
            r_lPFPaymentMethod_cnt = gPMFunctions.NullToLong(m_oDatabase.Parameters.Item("PFPaymentMethod_cnt").Value)

            Return result

        Catch excep As System.Exception

            result = gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMError

            ' Log Error Message
            bPMFunc.LogMessage(sUsername:=m_sUsername, iType:=gPMConstants.PMELogLevel.PMLogOnError, sMsg:="CheckSchemeType Failed", vApp:=ACApp, vClass:=ACClass, vMethod:="CheckSchemeType", vErrNo:=Informations.Err().Number, vErrDesc:=excep.Message, excep:=excep)

            Return result

        End Try
    End Function

    ' ***************************************************************** '
    ' Name: CheckTransactions
    '
    ' Description: Check if there are any transactions already for this plan
    '
    ' History: 29/11/2002 PSL - Created
    ' ***************************************************************** '
    Public Function CheckTransactions(ByVal v_lFinancePlanCnt As Integer, ByVal v_lFinancePlanVersion As Integer, ByRef r_nTransactionsExist As Integer) As Integer

        Dim result As Integer = 0
        Try

            result = gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMTrue

            ' Retrieve in house status for associated scheme
            m_oDatabase.Parameters.Clear()

            ' Finance plan cnt
            m_lReturn = m_oDatabase.Parameters.Add(sName:="financeplancnt", vValue:=gPMFunctions.ToSafeString(v_lFinancePlanCnt), iDirection:=gPMConstants.PMEParameterDirection.PMParamInput, iDataType:=gPMConstants.PMEDataType.PMLong)
            If m_lReturn <> gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMTrue Then
                Return m_lReturn
            End If

            ' Finance plan version
            m_lReturn = m_oDatabase.Parameters.Add(sName:="financeplanversion", vValue:=gPMFunctions.ToSafeString(v_lFinancePlanVersion), iDirection:=gPMConstants.PMEParameterDirection.PMParamInput, iDataType:=gPMConstants.PMEDataType.PMLong)
            If m_lReturn <> gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMTrue Then
                Return m_lReturn
            End If

            ' TransactionID return value
            m_lReturn = m_oDatabase.Parameters.Add(sName:="TransactionsExist", vValue:=gPMFunctions.ToSafeString(0), iDirection:=gPMConstants.PMEParameterDirection.PMParamOutput, iDataType:=gPMConstants.PMEDataType.PMInteger)
            If m_lReturn <> gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMTrue Then
                Return m_lReturn
            End If

            ' Execute the procedure

            m_lReturn = m_oDatabase.SQLAction(sSQL:="spu_PFCheckTransactions", sSQLName:="CheckTransactions", bStoredProcedure:=True)
            If m_lReturn <> gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMTrue Then
                Return m_lReturn
            End If

            ' Retrieve the return value
            r_nTransactionsExist = m_oDatabase.Parameters.Item("TransactionsExist").Value

            Return result

        Catch excep As System.Exception

            result = gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMError

            ' Log Error Message
            bPMFunc.LogMessage(sUsername:=m_sUsername, iType:=gPMConstants.PMELogLevel.PMLogOnError, sMsg:="CheckTransactions Failed", vApp:=ACApp, vClass:=ACClass, vMethod:="CheckTransactions", vErrNo:=Informations.Err().Number, vErrDesc:=excep.Message, excep:=excep)

            Return result

        End Try
    End Function

    'MKW120903 PF 3rd Party MTA START
    '*************************************************************************
    ' Name:         PostMTA_ThirdParty
    ' Description:  Called only from Finance Plan Maintenance
    '               Creates all the new plan version for an MTA.
    '               Created for Third Party mta's, supercedes previous and
    '                 transacts plan.
    ' History:      MKW120903
    '*************************************************************************
    Public Function PostMTA_ThirdParty(ByRef r_vPremiumFinance As Array, ByVal v_vTransArray(,) As Object, ByVal v_vOldPFArray As Array) As Integer

        Dim result As Integer = 0
        Const kMethodName As String = "PostMTA_ThirdParty"

        Dim lPremiumFinanceCnt, lPremiumFinanceVersion As Integer
        Dim cFinanceAmount As Decimal
        Dim iDayOfWeekOrMonth As Integer
        Dim bHasProtection As Boolean
        Dim dtStartDate, dtEndDate As Date
        Dim bIdentifiedScheme As Boolean
        Dim lPartyCnt As Integer
        Dim m_vQuoteArray(,) As Object = Nothing
        Dim lMode As Integer
        Dim vNewPFPlan As Object = Nothing
        Dim lCount As Integer
        Dim bSGQuote As Boolean
        Dim sICCS As String = String.Empty
        Dim sProviderCode As String = String.Empty

        Try

            result = gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMTrue

            bSGQuote = (gPMFunctions.ToSafeString(r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanProductClass, 0)).Trim() = "SG")

            lPremiumFinanceCnt = gPMFunctions.ToSafeInteger(r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanPFCnt, 0))

            lPremiumFinanceVersion = gPMFunctions.ToSafeInteger(r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanPFVersion, 0))

            lPartyCnt = gPMFunctions.ToSafeInteger(r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanClientId, 0))
            iDayOfWeekOrMonth = gPMFunctions.NullToInteger(r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanDayOfWeekOrMonth, 0))
            bHasProtection = gPMFunctions.NullToDecimal(r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanCostOfProtection, 0)) > 0

            If Not (bSGQuote) Then
                'Get NB Quote.

                m_lReturn = Calculate_Quotes(gPMFunctions.ToSafeInteger(r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanCompanyNo, 0)), "MTA", DateTime.Now, dtStartDate, dtEndDate, CDate("00:00:00"), iDayOfWeekOrMonth, iDayOfWeekOrMonth, cFinanceAmount, bHasProtection, -1, False, lPartyCnt, m_vQuoteArray, v_lInsuranceFileCnt:=gPMFunctions.ToSafeLong(r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanInsuranceFileCnt, 0), 0), r_lPremFinanceCnt:=lPremiumFinanceCnt, r_lPremFinanceVer:=lPremiumFinanceVersion, v_vPFTransArray:=v_vTransArray, v_bInHouse:=False)

                bIdentifiedScheme = False
                If Informations.IsArray(m_vQuoteArray) Then

                    For lCount = m_vQuoteArray.GetLowerBound(0) To m_vQuoteArray.GetUpperBound(0)

                        If gPMFunctions.ToSafeInteger(m_vQuoteArray(k_PFQuoteSchemeNo, lCount)) = gPMFunctions.ToSafeInteger(r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanSchemeNo, 0)) Then
                            'Identified Same Scheme.
                            bIdentifiedScheme = True
                            Exit For
                        End If
                    Next lCount
                End If
            End If

            If bIdentifiedScheme Or bSGQuote Then

                If Not (bSGQuote) Then
                    m_lReturn = InsertOrUpdatePremiumFinance(v_vQuoteArray:=m_vQuoteArray, v_lSelectedQuoteIndex:=lCount, v_vPFTransArray:=v_vTransArray, r_lPremiumFinanceCnt:=lPremiumFinanceCnt, r_lPremiumFinanceVer:=lPremiumFinanceVersion)
                    If m_lReturn <> gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMTrue Then
                        gPMFunctions.RaiseError("GetSingleFinancePlan", "v_lSelectedQuoteIndex:=" & lCount, gPMConstants.PMELogLevel.PMLogError)
                    End If

                    m_lReturn = GetSingleFinancePlan(v_lFinanceCount:=m_lPremFinanceCnt, v_lFinanceVersion:=lPremiumFinanceVersion, r_vPFPremiumFinance:=vNewPFPlan)
                    If m_lReturn <> gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMTrue Then
                        gPMFunctions.RaiseError("GetSingleFinancePlan", "v_lFinanceCount:=" & m_lPremFinanceCnt, gPMConstants.PMELogLevel.PMLogError)
                    End If

                    'Copy Bank Details

                    vNewPFPlan(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankName, 0) = r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankName, 0)

                    vNewPFPlan(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankSortCode, 0) = r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankSortCode, 0)

                    vNewPFPlan(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankAccountNo, 0) = r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankAccountNo, 0)

                    vNewPFPlan(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankAccountName, 0) = r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankAccountName, 0)

                    vNewPFPlan(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankBranch, 0) = r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankBranch, 0)

                    vNewPFPlan(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankAddress1, 0) = r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankAddress1, 0)

                    vNewPFPlan(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankAddress2, 0) = r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankAddress2, 0)

                    vNewPFPlan(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankAddress3, 0) = r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankAddress3, 0)

                    vNewPFPlan(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankTown, 0) = r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankTown, 0)

                    vNewPFPlan(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankAddress4, 0) = r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankAddress4, 0)

                    vNewPFPlan(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankPostcode, 0) = r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankPostcode, 0)

                    vNewPFPlan(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankCountry, 0) = r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankCountry, 0)

                    vNewPFPlan(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankCountry_ID, 0) = r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankCountry_ID, 0)

                    vNewPFPlan(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankAreaCode, 0) = r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankAreaCode, 0)

                    vNewPFPlan(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankPhone, 0) = r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankPhone, 0)

                    vNewPFPlan(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankExtn, 0) = r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankExtn, 0)

                    vNewPFPlan(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankFaxCode, 0) = r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankFaxCode, 0)

                    vNewPFPlan(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankFax, 0) = r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanBankFax, 0)

                    'Regenerate Finance Auto Reference
                    m_lReturn = GETICCS(sICCS)
                    If m_lReturn <> gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMTrue Then
                        sICCS = ""
                    End If

                    vNewPFPlan(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanFinCollPlanRef, 0) = StringsHelper.Format(gPMFunctions.ToSafeInteger(sICCS), "0000") & StringsHelper.Format(gPMFunctions.ToSafeInteger(vNewPFPlan(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanPFCnt, 0)), "0000") & StringsHelper.Format(gPMFunctions.ToSafeInteger(vNewPFPlan(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanPFVersion, 0)), "00")

                Else
                    vNewPFPlan = r_vPremiumFinance
                End If

                'Set New Version to Live.
                vNewPFPlan(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanStatusInd, 0) = bSIRPremFinConst.PFStatusIndLive
                m_lReturn = UpdateExistingRecord(vExistingRecord:=vNewPFPlan, vPremiumFinanceCnt:=lPremiumFinanceCnt, vPremiumFinanceVersion:=lPremiumFinanceVersion)
                If m_lReturn <> gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMTrue Then
                    gPMFunctions.RaiseError("UpdateExistingRecord", "vPremiumFinanceCnt:=" & lPremiumFinanceCnt, gPMConstants.PMELogLevel.PMLogError)
                End If

                m_lReturn = CreateEvent(v_lMode:=gPMFunctions.ToSafeString(m_iTask), v_lInsuranceFileCnt:=gPMFunctions.ToSafeLong(vNewPFPlan(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanInsuranceFileCnt, 0), 0), v_lPartyCnt:=gPMFunctions.ToSafeInteger(vNewPFPlan(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanClientId, 0)))
                If m_lReturn <> gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMTrue Then
                    gPMFunctions.RaiseError("UpdateExistingRecord", "vPremiumFinanceCnt:=" & lPremiumFinanceCnt, gPMConstants.PMELogLevel.PMLogError)
                End If

                lMode = 3

                If bSGQuote Then

                    m_lReturn = GetFinanceProviderDetails(v_lCompanyNo:=gPMFunctions.ToSafeLong(vNewPFPlan(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanCompanyNo, 0)), v_lSchemeNo:=gPMFunctions.ToSafeLong(vNewPFPlan(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanSchemeNo, 0)), v_lSchemeVersion:=gPMFunctions.ToSafeLong(vNewPFPlan(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanSchemeVersion, 0)), r_sShortName:=sProviderCode)
                    If m_lReturn <> gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMTrue Then
                        gPMFunctions.RaiseError("GetFinanceProviderDetails", "Failed", gPMConstants.PMELogLevel.PMLogError)
                    End If

                    If sProviderCode = "PCLSG" Then
                        If gPMFunctions.ToSafeString(vNewPFPlan(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanXSLCode, 0)).Trim() = "PCLSG" Or gPMFunctions.ToSafeString(vNewPFPlan(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanXSLCode, 0)).Trim() = "PCLPSG" Then
                            m_lReturn = ProcessPlan(lMode:=lMode, v_vPremiumFinanceArray:=vNewPFPlan, v_vTransArray:=v_vTransArray, v_iMTAType:=bSIRPremFinConst.m_klInstalmentMTAType_SGNoProcessTransact)
                            If m_lReturn <> gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMTrue Then
                                gPMFunctions.RaiseError("ProcessPlan", "lMode:=" & lMode, gPMConstants.PMELogLevel.PMLogError)
                            End If
                        Else
                            m_lReturn = ProcessPlan(lMode:=lMode, v_vPremiumFinanceArray:=vNewPFPlan, v_vTransArray:=v_vTransArray, v_iMTAType:=1)
                            If m_lReturn <> gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMTrue Then
                                gPMFunctions.RaiseError("ProcessPlan", "lMode:=" & lMode, gPMConstants.PMELogLevel.PMLogError)
                            End If
                        End If
                    End If
                Else
                    m_lReturn = ProcessPlan(lMode:=lMode, v_vPremiumFinanceArray:=vNewPFPlan, v_vTransArray:=v_vTransArray)
                    If m_lReturn <> gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMTrue Then
                        gPMFunctions.RaiseError("ProcessPlan", "lMode:=" & lMode, gPMConstants.PMELogLevel.PMLogError)
                    End If
                End If

                m_lReturn = StatusUpdate(vPremiumFinanceCnt:=lPremiumFinanceCnt, vPremiumFinanceVersion:=lPremiumFinanceVersion, vStatusInd:=bSIRPremFinConst.PFStatusIndLive)
                If m_lReturn <> gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMTrue Then
                    gPMFunctions.RaiseError("StatusUpdate", "vPremiumFinanceCnt:=" & lPremiumFinanceCnt, gPMConstants.PMELogLevel.PMLogError)
                End If

                r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanPFCnt, 0) = lPremiumFinanceCnt

                r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanPFVersion, 0) = lPremiumFinanceVersion

            Else
                Return gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMNotFound
            End If

            Return result
        Catch ex As Exception

            ' DO Not Call any functions before here or the error will be lost
            bPMFunc.LogError(v_sUsername:=m_sUsername, v_sClass:=ACClass, v_sMethod:=kMethodName, r_lFunctionReturn:=result, excep:=ex)

            ' If you want to rollback a transaction or something, do it here

        Finally

            ' Do any tidy up, e.g. Set x = Nothing here

            '		Return result

            ' This is for debugging only
            '		Resume 

            '		Return result
        End Try
        Return result
    End Function

    '*************************************************************************
    ' Name:         PostMTA
    ' Description:  Called only from Finance Plan Maintenance
    '               Creates all the new Instalments etc for an MTA. Deletes
    '               unpaid instalments for previous plans
    '               for each.
    ' History:      TR071102 - Created as per TS23 Section 4.2.1
    '*************************************************************************
    Public Function PostMTA(ByRef r_vPremiumFinance As Array, ByVal v_vTransArray(,) As Object, ByVal v_vOldPFArray As Array) As Integer

        Dim result As Integer = 0
        Const kMethodName As String = "PostMTA"

        Dim lPremiumFinanceCnt, lPremiumFinanceVersion As Integer
        Dim oACTInstalments As New bACTInstalments.Business
        Dim lLeadAgentCnt, lClientCnt As Integer
        Dim cAdjustment, cFee, cTax, cPlanOs As Decimal
        Dim lNewPlanTransID As Integer
        Dim cOldFee, cOldTax As Decimal
        Dim vOrionTransactions As Object = Nothing
        Dim cTransAmount As Decimal
        Dim cDepositAmount As Decimal
        Dim vSubAgents As Object = Nothing
        Try

            result = gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMTrue

            lPremiumFinanceCnt = gPMFunctions.ToSafeInteger(r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanPFCnt, 0))

            lPremiumFinanceVersion = gPMFunctions.ToSafeInteger(r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanPFVersion, 0))

            'Create an object for Orion

            oACTInstalments = New bACTInstalments.Business
            m_lReturn = oACTInstalments.Initialise(sUsername:=m_sUsername, sPassword:=m_sPassword, iUserID:=m_iUserID, iSourceID:=m_iSourceID, iLanguageID:=m_iLanguageID, iCurrencyID:=m_iCurrencyID, iLogLevel:=m_iLogLevel, sCallingAppName:=ACApp, vDatabase:=m_oDatabase)
            If m_lReturn <> gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMTrue Then
                gPMFunctions.RaiseError("gPMComponentServices.CreateBusinessObject", "v_sClassName:=bACTInstalments.Business", gPMConstants.PMELogLevel.PMLogError)
            End If

            'Get the outstanding amount due

            m_lReturn = oACTInstalments.GetPlanOS(v_lPlanTransDetailID:=gPMFunctions.ToSafeInteger(v_vOldPFArray(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanPlanTransactionID, 0)), r_cOS:=cPlanOs)
            If m_lReturn <> gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMTrue Then

                gPMFunctions.RaiseError("oACTInstalments.GetPlanOS", "v_lPlanTransDetailID:=" & gPMFunctions.ToSafeInteger(v_vOldPFArray(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanPlanTransactionID, 0)), gPMConstants.PMELogLevel.PMLogError)
            End If
            'cOldTax = CDec(v_vOldPFArray(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanTaxCost, 0))
            'cOldFee = CDec(v_vOldPFArray(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanInterestCost, 0))
            cTax = CDec(r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanTaxCost, 0))
            cFee = CDec(r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanFinanceCharge, 0)) + cTax
            cDepositAmount = CDec(r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanDeposit, 0))

            cTransAmount = 0
            ' get the adjustment amount to cancel out the MTA transactions
            m_lReturn = GetMTAAdjustmentAmount(v_lPremFinanceCnt:=lPremiumFinanceCnt, v_lPremFinanceVersion:=lPremiumFinanceVersion, r_crAdjustmentAmount:=cAdjustment)
            If m_lReturn <> gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMTrue Then
                gPMFunctions.RaiseError("GetMTAAdjustmentAmount", "v_lPremFinanceCnt:=" & lPremiumFinanceCnt, gPMConstants.PMELogLevel.PMLogError)
            End If

            'Make sure that there are transactions before working on them
            If Informations.IsArray(v_vTransArray) AndAlso cAdjustment <> 0 Then
                ReDim vOrionTransactions(v_vTransArray.GetUpperBound(1))
                For lCount As Integer = v_vTransArray.GetLowerBound(1) To v_vTransArray.GetUpperBound(1)
                    vOrionTransactions(lCount) = gPMFunctions.ToSafeString(v_vTransArray(0, lCount)) & "|" & gPMFunctions.ToSafeString(v_vTransArray(2, lCount))
                    cTransAmount = cTransAmount + gPMFunctions.ToSafeCurrency(v_vTransArray(2, lCount))
                Next
            End If

            m_lReturn = GetAgentAndClient(v_lPremFinanceCnt:=lPremiumFinanceCnt, v_lPremFinanceVersion:=lPremiumFinanceVersion, r_lLeadAgentCnt:=lLeadAgentCnt, r_lClientCnt:=lClientCnt)
            If m_lReturn <> gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMTrue Then
                gPMFunctions.RaiseError("GetAgentAndClient", "v_lPremFinanceCnt:=" & lPremiumFinanceCnt, gPMConstants.PMELogLevel.PMLogError)
            End If
            ' PN74429 - In case of MTA, sync the logic written under TransactPlanInHouse() to PostMTA()
            If r_vPremiumFinance(k_PFPlanTransactionType, 0).ToString().Trim().ToUpper() = "MTA" And cTransAmount <> 0 Then
                cAdjustment = gPMFunctions.ToSafeCurrency(r_vPremiumFinance(k_PFPlanTotalCost, 0)) - gPMFunctions.ToSafeCurrency(cPlanOs) - cTransAmount + (gPMFunctions.ToSafeCurrency(r_vPremiumFinance(k_PFPlanDeposit, 0)))
                cFee = gPMFunctions.ToSafeCurrency(r_vPremiumFinance(k_PFPlanTotalCost, 0)) - gPMFunctions.ToSafeCurrency(cPlanOs) - cTransAmount + (gPMFunctions.ToSafeCurrency(r_vPremiumFinance(k_PFPlanDeposit, 0)))
                cTax = gPMFunctions.ToSafeCurrency(r_vPremiumFinance(k_PFPlanTaxCost, 0))
            End If

            m_lReturn = GetSubAgents(lPremiumFinanceCnt, lPremiumFinanceVersion, vSubAgents)
            If m_lReturn <> gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMTrue Then
                gPMFunctions.RaiseError("GetAgentAndClient", "v_lPremFinanceCnt:=" & lPremiumFinanceCnt, gPMConstants.PMELogLevel.PMLogError)
            End If

            m_lReturn = oACTInstalments.PostMTAAdjustment(r_lNewPlanTransID:=lNewPlanTransID,
                                                          v_lPlanTransDetailID:=gPMFunctions.ToSafeInteger(v_vOldPFArray(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanPlanTransactionID, 0)),
                                                          v_vFinanceTrans:=vOrionTransactions,
                                                          v_cAdjustment:=cAdjustment,
                                                          v_cFee:=cFee,
                                                          v_cTax:=cTax,
                                                          v_cOSAmount:=cPlanOs,
                                                          v_lPremiumFinanceCnt:=lPremiumFinanceCnt,
                                                          v_lPremiumFinanceVersion:=lPremiumFinanceVersion,
                                                          v_lLeadAgentCnt:=lLeadAgentCnt,
                                                          v_cOldFee:=cOldFee,
                                                          v_cOldTax:=cOldTax,
                                                          v_lOrigianlPlanTransDetailID:=gPMFunctions.ToSafeInteger(v_vOldPFArray(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanPlanTransactionID, 0)),
                                                          v_bCommissionSpread:=(gPMFunctions.NullToLong(r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanCommissionSpread, 0)) = 1),
                                                           v_cNewPlanAmount:=CDec(r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanTotalCost, 0)),
                                                           v_cDeposit:=cDepositAmount,
                                                          v_bProcessDeposit:=Not CBool(r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanDepositAsInstalment, 0)), v_bSubAgentCommissionSpread:=(NullToLong(r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanSubAgentCommissionSpread, 0)) = 1), v_vSubAgent:=vSubAgents)

            If m_lReturn <> gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMTrue Then
                gPMFunctions.RaiseError("PostMTAAdjustment", "v_lPremiumFinanceCnt:=" & lPremiumFinanceCnt, gPMConstants.PMELogLevel.PMLogError)
            End If

            'Populate the TransID for this Premium Finance

            r_vPremiumFinance(bSIRPremFinConst.k_PFPlanPlanTransactionID, 0) = lNewPlanTransID
            Return result
        Catch ex As Exception

            ' DO Not Call any functions before here or the error will be lost
            bPMFunc.LogError(v_sUsername:=m_sUsername, v_sClass:=ACClass, v_sMethod:=kMethodName, r_lFunctionReturn:=result, excep:=ex)

            ' If you want to rollback a transaction or something, do it here

        Finally

            ' Do any tidy up, e.g. Set x = Nothing here
            If Not (oACTInstalments Is Nothing) Then

                oACTInstalments.Dispose()
                oACTInstalments = Nothing
            End If

        End Try
        Return result
    End Function

    ' RAW 11/03/2003 : ISS2580 : added
    ' ***************************************************************** '
    ' Name: BeginTrans (Private)
    '
    ' Description: Begins a Transaction.
    '
    ' ***************************************************************** '
    Public Function BeginTrans() As Integer

        Dim result As Integer = 0
        Try

            result = gPMConstants.PMEReturnCode.PMTrue

            ' Begin the Transaction
